name: KIRIK KIKIK
description:
KIRIK KIKIK

KIRIK KIKIK is the most dangerous wild animal robot in Nusaverse. Created in OBYØR Laboratory.

This robot created to maintain the stability of forest life. This robot is an experimental project. Made from mixing DNA from dogs and foxes, also injected with sharp vision ability and ultrasound technology. With glitching red eyes to light up the night, KIRIK KIKIK is a nocturnal robot.

Even though with his small body KIRIK KIKIK still very dangerous, he can eat bigger enemy.
